#Purpose:   This program will ask the user to input the file name including the extension
            #Then it will output whatever is after the period in the file name(extension)






name = input("What is the file name of your program (include the extension)?")      #This will ask the user to input the file name including the extension
n = name.find('.')                                                                  #This will find the period in the file name
print(name[n+1:])                                                                   #Finally, it will ouput whatever comes after the period in the file name(extension)
